{"tid":2404654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登再批特朗普疫苗工作不足","createTime":"2021-02-11T23:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T03:47:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cc196191eb82f308459eea429b4f58f2d8b76a23","tid":2404654,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T23:51:59.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登周四訪問馬里蘭州的疫苗實驗室，承認美國將無法在夏季結束前，為所有國民接種武肺疫苗。拜登批評前總統特朗普未有為疫苗做好準備，也沒訂購足夠疫苗，稱自己正在修正問題，呼籲國民繼續保持耐心。拜登同時宣佈，已分別從輝瑞及Moderna增購各1億劑疫苗，目前繼續是在7月底前取得足以讓3億人接種的疫苗數量。連同拜登最新宣佈訂購的2億劑疫苗在內，美國至今已訂購6億劑武肺疫苗。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210212/EO7XF6TUPZA47BV6SRE7BQYB6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210212%2FEO7XF6TUPZA47BV6SRE7BQYB6Y%2F&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=752cdb03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210212%2FEO7XF6TUPZA47BV6SRE7BQYB6Y%2F&h=8b0302e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210212/EO7XF6TUPZA47BV6SRE7BQYB6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"84822b585bbabd8ebbc5c7f7502163de18f36185","tid":2404654,"uid":391123,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T23:59:37.000Z","msg":"咸濕完細路買垃圾針拮吓人 鞭吓侵侵又過一日"},{"pid":"733c1218c44f81dfc8ec275a12d1301371c6d29f","tid":2404654,"uid":179775,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:00:01.000Z","msg":"你同班醫療公司夾埋做鳩侵專登唔講疫苗成功"},{"pid":"63ee07f264a06611a709189f6bb0dd493ca831e5","tid":2404654,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:02:00.000Z","msg":"上位前批侵上位，上左位就做好自己在位工作啦！不過佢唔知做到幾年，賀錦麗應該好快上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca46b4117cf1f575892d8ad7bf02b22fef2f389b","tid":2404654,"uid":130105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:02:50.000Z","msg":"訂咗都冇用，廠出到貨先得，不過笨左又打曬飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" c